SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from :1 h where h.pbh_status = 15 and h.pbh_periodiek_opdrachtnr > 0 and h.pbh_datum_eerstvolgende_opdr between '00010101' and ~2 and h.pbh_relatie between ~3 and ~4 and h.pbh_product between ~5 and ~6 and h.pbh_product_volgnr between ~7 and ~8 :9

select D.RELATIE from (select rownum "RIJ", C. RELATIE from (select h.pbh_relatie "RELATIE" from :1 h where h.pbh_status = 15 and h.pbh_periodiek_opdrachtnr > 0 and h.pbh_datum_eerstvolgende_opdr between '00010101' and ~2 and h.pbh_relatie between ~3 and ~4 and h.pbh_product between ~5 and ~6 and h.pbh_product_volgnr between ~7 and ~8 :9 order by h.pbh_relatie) C) D where MOD(D.RIJ, ~10) = 0
